items.name: Berries Summer Cupcakes
items.description: Delicious cupcakes perfect for summer gatherings. Made with a light and fluffy vanilla batter, topped with a mix of fresh berries including strawberries, blueberries, and raspberries. Ingredients: Flour, sugar, butter, eggs, vanilla extract, baking powder, salt, mixed berries.

items.name: Brownies Different Flavor
items.description: Indulge in the rich and fudgy goodness of our brownies with a twist. This assorted pack includes different flavors such as classic chocolate, walnut, and caramel swirl. Ingredients: Chocolate, butter, sugar, eggs, flour, cocoa powder, walnuts, caramel.

items.name: Butter Cookies
items.description: Melt-in-your-mouth buttery cookies that are perfect with a cup of tea or coffee. These classic cookies are made with simple ingredients like butter, sugar, and flour. Ingredients: Butter, sugar, flour, vanilla extract.

items.name: Cherry Jelly Cheesecake
items.description: A delightful cheesecake with a twist of cherry jelly. The creamy cheesecake is topped with a layer of sweet and tangy cherry jelly. Ingredients: Cream cheese, sugar, eggs, vanilla extract, graham cracker crust, cherry jelly.

items.name: Chocolate Blueberries Cake
items.description: A decadent chocolate cake loaded with fresh blueberries. The combination of rich chocolate and bursting blueberries creates a delightful flavor. Ingredients: Chocolate, flour, sugar, butter, eggs, cocoa powder, blueberries.

items.name: Chocolate Bonbons
items.description: Indulge in these bite-sized chocolate bonbons filled with various creamy centers. Flavors include hazelnut, raspberry, and caramel. Ingredients: Chocolate, cream, hazelnut, raspberry, caramel.

items.name: Chocolate Brownies
items.description: Classic chocolate brownies that are dense, fudgy, and irresistible. Made with high-quality cocoa and a generous amount of chocolate chunks. Ingredients: Chocolate, butter, sugar, eggs, flour, cocoa powder.

items.name: Chocolate Cookies
items.description: A chocolate lover's dream! These cookies are loaded with both cocoa powder and chunks of premium chocolate. Perfectly chewy with a rich chocolate flavor. Ingredients: Chocolate, butter, sugar, flour, cocoa powder.

items.name: Chocolate Cupcake
items.description: Indulge in the decadence of chocolate with these moist and fluffy chocolate cupcakes. Topped with a velvety chocolate frosting for an extra treat. Ingredients: Flour, sugar, butter, eggs, cocoa powder, baking powder, salt.

items.name: Chocolate Summer Berries Cake
items.description: An exquisite chocolate cake featuring a blend of summer berries. Layers of chocolate cake are filled with a luscious berry compote and frosted with chocolate ganache. Ingredients: Chocolate, flour, sugar, butter, eggs, mixed berries, ganache.

items.name: Classic Cheesecake
items.description: The timeless classic cheesecake with a buttery graham cracker crust and a smooth, creamy filling. Pure indulgence in every bite. Ingredients: Cream cheese, sugar, eggs, vanilla extract, graham cracker crust.

items.name: Cookies Cream Cake
items.description: A delightful cake that combines the goodness of cookies and cream. Layers of moist cake are sandwiched with a velvety cookies and cream frosting. Ingredients: Flour, sugar, butter, eggs, cookies, cream.

items.name: Easter Cupcakes
items.description: Celebrate Easter with these festive cupcakes. Topped with colorful frosting and edible decorations, they're a joyous addition to your holiday festivities. Ingredients: Flour, sugar, butter, eggs, vanilla extract, baking powder, salt, food coloring.

items.name: Fruit Cake
items.description: A classic fruit cake filled with a medley of dried fruits and nuts. Moist and flavorful, it's a perfect treat for any occasion. Ingredients: Flour, sugar, butter, eggs, mixed dried fruits, nuts.

items.name: Monster Theme Cake
items.description: A fun and whimsical cake perfect for birthdays or themed parties. Decorated with colorful frosting and edible monster-themed decorations. Ingredients: Flour, sugar, butter, eggs, vanilla extract, food coloring.

items.name: Muffin Devil Horns
items.description: Spice up your muffin experience with these devilishly delicious muffins. Featuring a hint of cinnamon and a devil horn-shaped decoration. Ingredients: Flour, sugar, butter, eggs, cinnamon.

items.name: Muffin Ghost
items.description: Adorable ghost-shaped muffins that are both cute and tasty. Perfect for Halloween or any spooky-themed occasion. Ingredients: Flour, sugar, butter, eggs, vanilla extract, baking powder, salt.

items.name: Pumpkin Spice Cupcakes
items.description: Embrace the flavors of fall with these pumpkin spice cupcakes. Infused with warm spices and topped with a luscious cream cheese frosting. Ingredients: Flour, sugar, butter, eggs, pumpkin puree, spices, cream cheese.
